			<div class="post-2499 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-gold-price-suppression-scheme tag-000-32356 tag-atomic-number-79 tag-bank-for-international-settlement tag-comex tag-gld tag-gld-prospectus tag-international-accounting-standards tag-presentation-currency tag-prospectus tag-slv post_box top" id="post-2499">
